/tr>\n  </table>\n\n  <h2 style="font-size:15px;margin:22px 0 4px;">Pre-workout options</h2>\n  \n    <div style="border:1px solid #e3e3e3;border-radius:8px;padding:14px;margin:8px 0;background:#fff;">\n      <div style="font-weight:600;font-size:15px;margin-bottom:4px;">Oatmeal with Banana and Almond Butter</div>\n      <div style="color:#666;font-size:12px;margin-bottom:8px;">8 min prep &middot; 121C / 24P / 14F &middot; 635 kcal</div>\n      <ul style="margin:6px 0 8px 18px;padding:0;font-size:13px;color:#333;"><li>50g rolled oats</li><li>240ml whole milk</li><li>1 medium (100g) banana</li><li>1 tablespoon (16g) almond butter</li><li>1 teaspoon (7g) honey</li></ul>\n      <div style="font-size:12px;color:#555;font-style:italic;">Familiar comfort food with easily digestible carbs, adequate protein, and minimal fiber to fuel a 100-minute hard ride without GI distress.</div>\n    </div>\n    <div style="border:1px solid #e3e3e3;border-radius:8px;padding:14px;margin:8px 0;background:#fff;">\n      <div style="font-weight:600;font-size:15px;margin-bottom:4px;">Turkey and White Bread Toast with Honey</div>\n      <div style="color:#666;font-size:12px;margin-bottom:8px;">5 min prep &middot; 123C / 24P / 11F &middot; 628 kcal</div>\n      <ul style="margin:6px 0 8px 18px;padding:0;font-size:13px;color:#333;"><li>2 slices (56g) white bread</li><li>60g turkey breast (deli)</li><li>1.5 tablespoon (21g) honey</li><li>0.5 tablespoon (7g) butter</li></ul>\n      <div style="font-size:12px;color:#555;font-style:italic;">Simple, familiar protein source with refined carbs for quick absorption, minimal fiber, and low fat for easy digestion before intense effort.</div>\n    </div>\n\n  <h2 style="font-size:15px;margin:22px 0 4px;">Post-workout options</h2>\n  \n    <div style="border:1px solid #e3e3e3;border-radius:8px;padding:14px;margin:8px 0;background:#fff;">\n      <div style="font-weight:600;font-size:15px;margin-bottom:4px;">Grilled Chicken Breast with White Rice and Olive Oil</div>\n      <div style="color:#666;font-size:12px;margin-bottom:8px;">25 min prep &middot; 82C / 48P / 16F &middot; 626 kcal</div>\n      <ul style="margin:6px 0 8px 18px;padding:0;font-size:13px;color:#333;"><li>150g chicken breast</li><li>150g white rice (cooked)</li><li>1 tablespoon (15g) extra-virgin olive oil</li><li>0.5 teaspoon sea salt</li></ul>\n      <div style="font-size:12px;color:#555;font-style:italic;">High-protein Mediterranean staple with fast-digesting rice carbs to replenish glycogen and olive oil for micronutrient absorption and satiety.</div>\n    </div>\n    <div style="border:1px solid #e3e3e3;border-radius:8px;padding:14px;margin:8px 0;background:#fff;">\n      <div style="font-weight:600;font-size:15px;margin-bottom:4px;">Greek Yogurt with Granola and Berries</div>\n      <div style="color:#666;font-size:12px;margin-bottom:8px;">3 min prep &middot; 81C / 24P / 12F &middot; 564 kcal</div>\n      <ul style="margin:6px 0 8px 18px;padding:0;font-size:13px;color:#333;"><li>200g Greek yogurt (plain, full-fat)</li><li>40g granola (low-fiber)</li><li>80g blueberries</li><li>1 tablespoon (14g) honey</li></ul>\n      <div style="font-size:12px;color:#555;font-style:italic;">Convenient, protein-rich recovery meal with fast carbs from granola and fruit to trigger glycogen resynthesis and muscle protein synthesis.</div>\n    </div>\n  \n\n  <div style="margin-top:24px;color:#999;font-size:11px;">Generated by n8n &middot; intervals.icu + Claude</div>\n</div>\n</body></html>
